# MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult

**Enumeration**

An item that represents one of the top results in a library search response.

## Declaration

```swift
enum TopResult
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult.album(_:)**: An item that corresponds to an album.
- **MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult.artist(_:)**: An item that corresponds to an artist.
- **MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult.musicVideo(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a music video.
- **MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult.playlist(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a playlist.
- **MusicLibrarySearchResponse.TopResult.song(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a song.

## Instance Properties

- **artwork**: The artwork of this top result for library search.
- **id**: The unique identifier of this item.
- **title**: The title of this top result for library search.
